==Useful Info==
'''Putrid demonspawn''' are demonspawn with a passive ability similar to the [[Powered by Death]] demonspawn mutation. They can be found in the [[Pandemonium]] and guarding it's portals in the [[Depths]].

==Tips & Tricks==
Try to get them in an area without [[corpse]]s, as nearby corpses will increase their regeneration rate. Try not to use poison against them unless you have access to lethal poison, since they have weak [[poison resistance]]. Like all demonspawn, they are also vulnerable to holy weapons and [[silver]], so use those if you have them.

==History==
*Putrid demonspawn were removed in [[0.19]]
*Putrid demonspawn were added in [[0.14]].

